THK已是芸芸電視台中立場中立，節目質素也比其餘電視台高。<br />\n<br />\n本人在此想向港台記者及員工表達萬分感謝，港台一直堅守自己崗位，謹守傳媒應有嘅價值觀，作為社會嘅第四權協助市民監察公權力。香港電台製作高質素的節目，如頭條新聞、鏗鏘集、五夜講場等等的節目，都給了香港的觀眾一個多角度的思維。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台在這幾個月，不斷有人向港台施加壓力，更包圍港台的大廈。這是對香港新聞價值自由的踐踏，本人在此希望貴局可以增加香港電台資源，令香港市民可以有一個較為中立的角度接收新聞訊息。"},{"pid":"6e82fc1c0a1ed31a8fecf5cfc729ef5747070bcf","tid":1885005,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T06:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c015c6f02afac7a48cd5733f8781caa51a271c","tid":1885005,"uid":264887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3171a44dd4adc9ab518b8f3d0bab617d88d264d","tid":1885005,"uid":216178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T06:54:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0611def4262e1a7c0e14bbdc721b2b54701fae2c","tid":1885005,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"112c94444068246b61ad8cb2fd38969b3c067f05","tid":1885005,"uid":53105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4c9e61251212800a388a1535c05295d0974a30c","tid":1885005,"uid":226850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:10:33.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"c2579fcb1a73f453a68d9d392c98d891cc175901","tid":1885005,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:12:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得寄俾商經局冇用<br />\n佢地實當睇唔到<br />\n直接寄俾港台好過"},{"pid":"3e8a6014753f5fd1b05080082d06cfaa40f90fb7","tid":1885005,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"已腥"},{"pid":"b7979f778e9f783872323222823565273a923218","tid":1885005,"uid":278037,"like":0,"dislike":0,